channel.title: MARBLED GLASS - Xiejra [first Auxy 5 song]
channel.description:
Hello and welcome to Auxy 5! Little bit more of a chilled out song, some hybrid “Alon Mor” samples I made a while back! Really tried to use the sample library to the best i could! (so much to explore) good job guys on the update! very happy you’re partnering with Black octopus sounds!
anyway hope you enjoy! https://soundcloud.com/xiejramusic/marbled-glass
~X
